{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"64445bb3ad","title":"中央文革关于新华社问题的通知","origin":"1967年7月4日新华社革命联合委员会主办《新闻战线》第2版","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6ce886292c","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":14,"articleId":"64445bb3ad"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"aa048f8141","name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"87dfa5c6ff","name":"中央文革"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8b5fcb2299","type":"title","text":"中央文革关于新华社问题的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"64445bb3ad"},{"id":"cea6e381e5","type":"authors","text":"中央文革","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"64445bb3ad"},{"id":"f7466cf8c1","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）新华社是党中央直属的宣传机构，不得由社内或社外的革命群众组织进行夺权和接管。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"64445bb3ad"},{"id":"680fa68ebb","type":"paragraph","text":"领导机构和人员的调整，要由党中央决定或批准。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"64445bb3ad"},{"id":"8c13e460ea","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）新华社已经建立的监督小组，要切实加以改进。这个问题，应由社内各革命群众组织协商解决。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"64445bb3ad"},{"id":"87f3da1d0c","type":"paragraph","text":"在没有妥善解决之前，都不要进驻社长办公室。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"64445bb3ad"},{"id":"569d90ab3f","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）主持新华社常务工作的副社长王唯真同志，有职有权。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"64445bb3ad"},{"id":"cce4983a83","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）立即成立临时工作小组，……，协助王唯真同志工作。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"64445bb3ad"},{"id":"9f94606e3d","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）一切工作同志都要坚守岗位，遵守纪律，抓革命，促工作，保证完成党和国家的任务。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"64445bb3ad"},{"id":"42a2d430a7","type":"paragraph","text":"（六）关于规章制度问题，可以批评、批判，提出改革建议，但要上极领导机关批准，才能实行。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"64445bb3ad"},{"id":"3ba2e60201","type":"appellation","text":"","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"64445bb3ad"}],"page":{"id":"abb1efaa22","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"64445bb3ad","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}